<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink373">
<l>niṉaittoṟuṅ kaliḻu miṭumpai yeytuka</l>
<l>pulikkōṭ piḻaitta kavaikkōṭṭu mutukalai</l>
<l>māṉpiṇai yaṇaitara vāṇkural viḷikkum</l>
<l>veñcura meṉmaka ḷuytta</l>
<l>vampamai valvil viṭalai tāyē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>May the mother attain sorrow</l>
<l>and cry whenever she recalls [her son],</l>
<l>the warrior with a strong bow, fit for arrows,</l>
<l>who led my daughter through the hot desert, </l>
<l>where old deer with forked horns</l>
<l>has escaped the grasp of a tiger</l>
<l>and calls for [his] doe with manly voice to join [him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
